citeinfo.title: County Boundaries for the State of Idaho Redistricting 2001 Process

descript.abstract: This data set reflects county boundaries for Idaho. Numerous demographic attributes are included.
descript.purpose: The primary use of the data set is for Idaho's 2001 Redistricting Process. This data set was compiled by Spatial Dynamics at the direction of the Idaho Legislative Services Office for use as the State's county Redistricting 2001 data set. No responsibility is assumed by the Idaho Legislative Services Office in the use of these data.

srcinfo.srccontr: County Boundary 2000 TIGER/Line files from the U.S. Census Bureau in Geographic Projection--Decimal Degrees, NAD83. A CD containing the TIGER/Line files was provided to Spatial Dynamic by the Idaho Legislative Services Office. Additionally, the P.L. 94-171 data were provided in the same manner.

procstep.procdesc: Data were processed by Spatial Dynamics

The files listed below were copied off of the computer provided to the University of Idaho Library by the Idaho Legislative Services Office for the Redistricting 2001 process (the files were from the update disc received on May 21, 2001). The files were then archived using tar & gzip compression. Lastly, the archived file was copied to the INSIDE Idaho server.

overview.eaover:
County boundaries are depicted as polygons with numerous attributes.
A data dictionary (provided by Spatial Dynamics) containing attribute definitions can be found at: http://cloud.insideidaho.org/data/ilso/DataDictionary17May.pdf
